      'ðŸ‘¤ Ticket assigned to',
      'ðŸ‘¤ Ticket unassigned.',
      'âš¡ Support team changed priority to',
      'â­', // Rating messages contain star emojis
      'Status changed to',
      'Priority changed to',
      'Ticket closed'
